title: Russia's War-Blood Upon The Snow - Season 1
description:
Russia's War-Blood Upon The Snow - Season 1

This is a massive and extremely well integrated series of documentaries that exhaustively depicts, explains, and examines the nature of the Soviet society at the time of the great patriotic struggle (as they called it) against the Nazi forces that invaded Russia during World War Two.

Ep 1 - The Darkness Descends
Ep 2 - The Hour Before Midnight
Ep 3 - The Goths Ride East
Ep 4 - Between Life & Death
Ep 5 - The Fight From Within
Ep 6 - The Cauldron Boils
Ep 7 - The Citadel
Ep 8 - False Dawn
Ep 9 - The Fall Of The Swastika
Ep 10 - The Cult Of Personality
